---
/**
 * Seal.astro — the sealed/gated stamp (brief §5, §7, §9).
 *
 * The ONLY place the accent red is allowed. Marks a gated crate as sealed but
 * still visible (curiosity, not a wall). Pass 1 stub: a static stamp glyph; the
 * ink-drawn tape + the seal-unravel reward animation arrive later.
 */
---

<span class="seal" role="img" aria-label="sealed — passcode required">SEALED</span>

<style>
  .seal {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-xs);
    right: var(--space-xs);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 0.15em 0.5em;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 3px;
    transform: rotate(-8deg);
  }
</style>
